{% block content %}
  <p class="nhsuk-body">The main scope of this project is to streamline traditional UI stack (<b>HTML + CSS + JS</b>) workflows and incorporate best practices for UI development when building <a href="https://service-manual.nhs.uk/design-system">NHSUK</a> or <a href="https://design-system.service.gov.uk/">GOVUK</a> digital services.</p>
  
  <p class="nhsuk-body">This project uses <a href="https://gulpjs.com/">Gulp 4</a>, <a href="https://webpack.js.org/">Webpack 4</a>, <a href="https://github.com/sass/node-sass">Node SASS</a>, <a href="https://babeljs.io/docs/en/">Babel</a> to build production-ready front-end assets using the <a href="https://github.com/nhsuk/nhsuk-frontend">NHSUK</a> or <a href="https://github.com/alphagov/govuk-frontend">GOVUK</a> front-end toolkit - or no toolkit at all if you need a blank canvas for your project.</p>
  
  <div class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-7">
    {{ actionLink({
      "text": "Find out more about this project",
      "href": "https://github.com/robertpataki/sprint-ui"
    }) }}
  </div>

  <div class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-5">
    <hr>
    {{ warningCallout({
      "heading": "This is not the official NHSUK prototyping toolkit.",
      "HTML": '<p class="nhsuk-body">You can use this project to build or prototype a NHSUK service, but it is important to note that this is not the <a href="https://nhsuk-prototype-kit.azurewebsites.net/docs">official NHSUK prototyping kit</a>, and it is <b>not</b> maintained by GDS.</p>'
    }) }}
  </div>

  <div class="nhsuk-u-margin-top-5">
    <hr>
    <p class="nhsuk-body">(Oh, by the way, today's date is <span data-module="todays-date">...</span>)</p>
  </div>
